So please rest your over active brains and use that same energy for some social work... Have a happy fun filled Sunday everyone…".There is nothing wrong in Renu Desai mentioning her ex-husband Pawan Kalyan's name whenever she wishes to speak about him and critics needn't be too harsh in such matters.
